    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Also reproduced with tip of master.\r\n\r\n```\r\n$ sudo mkdir /opt/grpc\r\n$ git clone --recursive git@github.com:grpc/grpc\r\n$ cd grpc\r\n$ git describe\r\nv1.12.1-4984-ga0e06fdac4\r\n$ make shared prefix=/opt/grpc\r\n$ sudo chown $LOGNAME /opt/grpc\r\n$ make install prefix=/opt/grpc\r\n$ ldd /opt/grpc/lib/libgrpc++.so.1\r\n        linux-vdso.so.1 (0x00007ffde8b07000)\r\n        libgrpc.so.7 => not found\r\n        libstdc++.so.6 => /usr/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libstdc++.so.6 (0x00007f07f5cb3000)\r\n...\r\n```"
