    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "So, we've been really relying on people's ld.conf system to solve this for us. I am not THAT much an expert, and I don't necessarily have strong opinions, but my solution to issues similar to the ones you're describing always has been for me to drop a line in /etc/ld.so.conf.d/ somewhere and rerun `ldconfig`.\r\n\r\nI'm actually fine with #18183, provided it doesn't break existing usage."
